@page "/Privacy"

<MarketingHero Title="Privacy"
               Highlight="policy"
               Subtitle="What we collect, how we use it, and how to control your data." />

<div class="Card">
    <h2 class="CardTitle">What we collect</h2>
    <p>Account email, password hash (bcrypt), uploaded credentials (CDL, TWIC, medical), location during active shifts, transaction history.</p>
    <h2 class="CardTitle" style="margin-top:18px">How we use it</h2>
    <p>To run the platform — match drivers to jobs, process payments, dispatch trucks. We never sell your data.</p>
    <h2 class="CardTitle" style="margin-top:18px">Your rights</h2>
    <p>Request export, correction, or deletion at <a href="mailto:privacy@wolfstruckingco.com">privacy@wolfstruckingco.com</a>. We respond in 30 days.</p>
</div>
